---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Marteso — The ASO Platform for Mobile Teams"
  description="Marteso is built by mobile developers who got tired of guessing. We make App Store Optimization data-driven, automated, and accessible for every team size."
  canonicalPath="/about"
>
  <div class="about-wrap">
    <div class="about-hero">
      <div class="section-label">About</div>
      <h1>We build the tool we always needed</h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">
        Marteso started as an internal tool. We were building mobile apps,
        spending hours every week manually checking keyword rankings, copying
        metadata between spreadsheets, and reacting to competitor moves days too
        late. At some point we realized the tooling was the problem — so we
        fixed it.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="mission-section">
      <div class="mission-label">Mission</div>
      <h2>Make organic growth measurable and repeatable</h2>
      <p>
        Most mobile teams treat ASO as a one-time setup task: write a
        description, pick some keywords, move on. They're leaving downloads on
        the table every single day. We built Marteso to change that — to make
        ongoing ASO as systematic and data-driven as any other growth channel.
      </p>
      <p>
        We track over 2.4 million keywords across the App Store and Google Play.
        We analyze competitor metadata in real time. We flag ranking drops
        before they compound into real losses. And we do all of this so that
        mobile teams can stop guessing and start compounding.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon">01</div>
        <h3>Data over intuition</h3>
        <p>
          Every recommendation Marteso makes is backed by real ranking data. We
          show you the numbers, not just the conclusion — so you can develop
          genuine ASO intuition over time, not just dependency on a tool.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon">02</div>
        <h3>Speed over perfection</h3>
        <p>
          The App Store rewards velocity. Teams that iterate keyword strategy
          monthly consistently outperform teams that do it quarterly, even when
          the quarterly updates are more carefully crafted. Marteso is designed
          to make fast iteration the path of least resistance.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon">03</div>
        <h3>Transparency over magic</h3>
        <p>
          We don't sell a black box. When Marteso surfaces a recommendation, we
          show you the signal that triggered it, the data behind it, and an
          honest estimate of the expected impact. You decide. We inform.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon">04</div>
        <h3>Built for builders</h3>
        <p>
          Marteso is made for indie developers, small mobile teams, and
          growth-focused companies who care deeply about their product. We don't
          build for enterprise procurement processes — we build for people who
          are actually in App Store Connect every week.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="fringelo-section">
      <div class="fringelo-inner">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Part of</div>
          <h2>The Fringelo ecosystem</h2>
          <p>
            Marteso is built and operated by Fringelo Group — a small team of
            developers and product people who build focused software tools for
            app creators. Fringelo's mission is to give independent developers
            access to the same quality of tooling that large companies build
            internally.
          </p>
          <p>
            We're based in Europe, bootstrapped, and obsessively focused on
            building tools that earn their place in your workflow.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://fringelo.com/"
            class="btn btn-ghost"
            style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-top:8px;"
            >Visit fringelo.com ↗</a
          >
        </div>
        <div class="fringelo-stat-stack">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-number">2.4M+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Keywords tracked</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-number">140+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">App Store markets</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-number">2024</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Founded</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-section">
      <h2>Ready to grow organic downloads?</h2>
      <p>
        Start for free. No credit card required. One app, 50 keywords, forever.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a
          href="https://marteso.com/app/signup/"
          class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Start free</a
        >
        <a href="/team" class="btn btn-ghost btn-large">Meet the team →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-wrap {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 140px 32px 120px;
  }

  .about-hero {
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 52px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .hero-lead {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin: 64px 0;
  }

  .mission-section {
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .mission-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .mission-section h2 {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .mission-section p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 32px;
  }

  .value-icon {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .value-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .fringelo-section {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .fringelo-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .fringelo-section .section-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .fringelo-section h2 {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .fringelo-section p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .fringelo-stat-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 140px;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 64px 0 0;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-wrap {
      padding: 120px 20px 80px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
    }
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .fringelo-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .fringelo-stat-stack {
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
